            "inline": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "Convert the input to an array."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Summary"
      },
      {
        "blocks": [
          {
            "items": [
              {
                "body_blocks": [
                  {
                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "Input data, in any form that can be converted to an array.  This\nincludes lists, lists of tuples, tuples, tuples of tuples, tuples\nof lists and ndarrays."
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "data_type": "array_like",
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "Input data, in any form that can be converted to an array.  This\nincludes lists, lists of tuples, tuples, tuples of tuples, tuples\nof lists and ndarrays."
                  }
                ],
                "name": "a",
                "type": "field_list"
              },
              {
                "body_blocks": [
                  {
                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "By default, the data-type is inferred from the input data."
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "data_type": "data-type, optional",
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "By default, the data-type is inferred from the input data."
                  }
                ],
                "name": "dtype",
                "type": "field_list"
              },
              {
                "body_blocks": [
                  {
                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "The memory layout of the output.\n'C' gives a row-major layout (C-style),\n'F' gives a column-major layout (Fortran-style).\n'C' and 'F' will copy if needed to ensure the output format.\n'A' (any) is equivalent to 'F' if input a is non-contiguous or Fortran-contiguous, otherwise, it is equivalent to 'C'.\nUnlike 'C' or 'F', 'A' does not ensure that the result is contiguous.\n'K' (keep) is the default and preserves the input order for the output."
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "data_type": "{'C', 'F', 'A', 'K'}, optional",
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "The memory layout of the output.\n'C' gives a row-major layout (C-style),\n'F' gives a column-major layout (Fortran-style).\n'C' and 'F' will copy if needed to ensure the output format.\n'A' (any) is equivalent to 'F' if input a is non-contiguous or Fortran-contiguous, otherwise, it is equivalent to 'C'.\nUnlike 'C' or 'F', 'A' does not ensure that the result is contiguous.\n'K' (keep) is the default and preserves the input order for the output."
                  }
                ],
                "name": "order",
                "type": "field_list"
              },
              {
                "body_blocks": [
                  {
                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "The device on which to place the created array. Default: "
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "code",
                        "text": "None"
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": ".\nFor Array-API interoperability only, so must be "
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "code",
                        "text": "\"cpu\""
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": " if passed."
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "argument_inline": [],
                    "content_blocks": [],
                    "directive": "versionadded",
